metadata.name: Day Dreams
metadata.description:
My collection of 1/1 images taken in Southern California featuring ordinary places and businesses that get visited, driven by, or worked in by people everyday. I'm drawn to the design of these buildings/places, their colors and flaws. The simple, mundane and dream like qualities in them that goes mostly unnoticed until presented in a particular light. 

Photographer/Artist: Benji Stein

Collection: Dream Days 

Edition: 1/1
